  "description": "Copper damascene electroplating for semiconductor interconnects using acid sulfate bath with accelerator/suppressor/leveler additives for bottom-up via and trench fill. Nickel, gold, and tin plating for electronics. Pulse reverse plating for sub-100 nm features. Operating at 5-40 mA/cm², 0.3-1.5V cell voltage, 20-25°C bath temperature.",
